{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ev-rental-go-api-tests-sprint3",
    "name": "EV Rental GO — Sprint 3 Integration Tests",
    "description": "Sprint 3 Integration Tests — Real-Time Fleet, WebSocket, Geofencing\n\n▶ วิธีใช้\n1. Import Collection + Environment (EV Rental GO — Local Dev)\n2. เลือก Environment ที่มุมขวาบน\n3. รัน folder ตามลำดับ: Auth → Positions → Alerts → Users Directory → Geofences → Vehicle-Zone Assignment → Breach Detection\n4. IDs จะ auto-save จาก response\n\n⚠️ ก่อนรัน Breach Detection folder:\n   - เริ่ม GPS Simulator ก่อน: pnpm sim:gps\n   - ตรวจสอบว่า Next.js server รันอยู่: pnpm dev\n\n🔌 WebSocket Test (ทำใน Browser — ไม่ใช่ Postman)\n   เปิด Browser Console แล้วรัน:\n   const ws = new WebSocket('ws://localhost:3000/api/fleet/ws');\n   ws.onmessage = e => console.log(JSON.parse(e.data));",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ─── Auto-inject session cookie on every request ───────────────",
          "const token = pm.environment.get('sessionToken');",
          "if (token) {",
          "  pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'Cookie', value: 'session=' + token });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ─── Auto-capture session cookie on every response ─────────────",
          "const setCookie = pm.response.headers.get('Set-Cookie');",
          "if (setCookie) {",
          "  const match = setCookie.match(/session=([^;]+)/);",
          "  if (match) pm.environment.set('sessionToken', match[1]);",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth — Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login as Super Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
